│   │   │   │   │                                    # level increment and +1 heart (capped at 6) are
│   │   │   │   │                                    # stored as pendingLevelUp in SingleplayerContext
│   │   │   │   │                                    # and applied before the next round begins — this
│   │   │   │   │                                    # ensures that if the player takes a hit on the
│   │   │   │   │                                    # same tick that a bot kill triggers a level-up,
│   │   │   │   │                                    # the heart is still granted before round restart;
