## CSS file placement rules

| File type | Gets CSS? | Pattern |
|---|---|---|
| Page (`page.tsx`) | Yes | `page.module.css` co-located in the same route folder |
| `layout.tsx` / `not-found.tsx` | Yes | `layout.module.css` / `not-found.module.css` co-located |
| UI component | Yes | Own named folder — `Name/Name.tsx` + `Name/Name.module.css` |
| Hook | No | Flat `.ts` file, no folder |
| Service | No | Flat `.ts` file, no folder |
| Context / Provider | No | Flat `.ts` / `.tsx` file, no folder |
| Physics / rendering / singleplayer logic | No | Flat `.ts` file, no folder |
| Types | No | Flat `.ts` file, no folder |
| `globals.css` | — | Design tokens, CSS reset, base document rules, and `@keyframes` definitions only — no component styles |

